  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Requires managed care providers and the medical assistance program shall cover prescription drugs approved by the federal food and drug administration for chronic weight management in adults with obesity with at least one weight-related condition."
